data.text:
Image Library

Download high-resolution images of the American Women Quarters for use in publications. Read the Mint’s design use policies and other information regarding the use of these images.

For more information about these coins, visit the American Women Quarters Program page. Shop the coin program or subscribe to the series on the U.S. Mint’s online catalog.
